<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="7Jan1924"><font color="red">7 January 1924</font> <i>BLHW</i> (to Harriet Weaver): Here is what I managed to get done. The pieces divided by a red line are not consecutive. There are three longish pieces in between. The first one is nearly finished &hellip; I hope you will like the enclosed pieces. I am afraid to stop writing. </div>
